photon相关
Photon is an off-chain scaling solution, enabling instant, low-fee and scalable payments.
It’s complementary to the Ethereum blockchain and Spectrum blockchain and works with ERC20 compatible token and ERC223 compatible token.
Photon currently can works on Windows, Linux ,Android, iOS etc.
Photon adds some new functions in version 1.0, such as , cooperative settlement,withdraw without closing the channel,channel charging and more perfect third-party services( Photon Monitoring and Photon-Path-Finder).
In order to improve the user experience and to better fit for the mobile network, Photon adopts the Matrix communication mechanism and supports the crash recovery and channel charging function.
Photon是一种链下扩展解决方案，可实现即时，低费用和可扩展的支付。
它是以太坊区块链和光谱区块链的补充，可与ERC20兼容Token和ERC223兼容Token配合使用。
Photon目前可以在Windows，Linux，Android，iOS等上运行.
Photon在1.0版本中添加了一些新功能，例如，合作解决，withdraw而不关闭频道，频道收费和更完美的第三方服务（Photon Monitoring and Photon-Path-Finder）。
为了改善用户体验并更好地适应移动网络，Photon采用Matrix通信机制，支持崩溃恢复和通道充电功能。

